subject: Basketball (College)
lead_paragraph: Kaleena Mosqueda-Lewis scored 21 points while Kelly Faris added 18 points and 12 rebounds to help No. 3 Connecticut beat No. 4 Duke, 79-49, in Storrs, Conn.
